Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:26.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:37.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:45.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:51.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:58.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.43,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:12.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:19.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:26.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:37.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:45.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:26.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:37.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:45.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:51.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:58.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:12.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:19.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:26.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:37.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:45.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:58.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#25  再生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲·阿爾馬克！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該感謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以能得到這能力  都是因為我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了我  引導我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在又打算在我面前扮演神嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼想支配人類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣做的話人類就無法停止戰爭從而滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是救世主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願一同前進  也不願相互理解嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和人類以自己的意願管理動物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…  戰勝成為純種的你的話  我的必要性就不可動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你的自私扭曲了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所引發的再生就由我來破壞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的覺悟嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO-Raiser！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲加農！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（李本茲的機體名字 同時也是在惡搞高達0079中的機體 RX-77  Guncannon 鋼加農）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲·阿爾馬克！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀發來了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀發來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  脫離了吠陀支援的新型機正在與OO-Raiser交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說新型機？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密要出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾恩先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掩護刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  準備炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞  能出擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密發來通信  托勒密發來通信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離充電完成還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是我所擅長的距離了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別以為只有你們才有Twin-Drive系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這部機體才是引導人類的Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來掩護你  李本茲·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有吠陀的支援  區區人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵復活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要戰鬥  我們的行動關係到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這種機體  就想找我挑戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:07:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有系統的幫助  改革者也不過如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是依靠著吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能戰勝我們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救我  李本茲！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混賬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這種攻擊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎部分被直接命中  航行…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刹那也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用這種障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是如今的刹那的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是純種的力量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  TRANS-AM的情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使用1秒！  能使用1秒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞…亞琉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  擊毀敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的敵機只有那台Gundam型的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  能聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你做好發射R2的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  備用的Drive…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快執行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這種力量  是因為受了原型GN-Drive的恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不是這樣的話我被製造出來就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連存在的意義也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞·埃德！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用吠陀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是引導人類  而是同人類一起創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我們改良者應該走的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和下等的人類一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你一直這樣俯視別人  才無法理解！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒這個打算！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然量子化了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於得到原型太陽爐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了這個  我就能成為伊奧利亞計劃的體現者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  甚至能成為超越體現者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體損傷太嚴重了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…  命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能夠戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp100}　{\fsp1}Matching clear{\r}\NGN Drive  裝配完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪  在哪裡  刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難  難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮  開闢未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你區區人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你沒有讀到這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想寫下自己對你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為克魯吉斯的少年兵  被迫踏上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得只能生活在戰場上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望和平的心情  我和你都一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可為什麼我和你所走的路  卻沒有任何交點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你通過武力  想要消滅世界上的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那能夠得以實現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的幸福又在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著罪責  身受傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  你還在繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的生活方式  令我不由自主地感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自己心中的幸福與他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有通過將這循環擴大  才能得到真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  也請你無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要抓住你自己的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  我祈禱著你能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下  到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿扎迪斯坦接受了地球聯邦政府的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於得以重建家園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能將支援擴大至中東各國  我將繼續努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  我會讓這小小的和平蔓延開的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像故事被人們口耳相傳那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像歌聲沁入人們的心中那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經侵蝕路易絲身體的細胞異常  現在已經徹底被抑制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是否也是多虧了刹那所發出的那道光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不知道真相和原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  她現在就在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新任聯邦總統
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有卡塔隆的各位也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣佈  將解散重複著屠殺行為 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並控制情報隱藏了這一事實的獨立治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並著手開始將地球聯邦軍重新編制
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外將通過援助非聯邦參加國  以及推進其加入聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著樹立真正意義上的地球聯邦而不懈努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  世界就改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過這也才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠相互理解  攜手共進的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用話語表達是很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們必須以此為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了將來誕生的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對  克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要從我們開始改變才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了樹立真正意義上的地球聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以三個嶄新的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的世界會是什麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我們不能再對世界不聞不問了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在和平中的我們  得知了現實與戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了它們的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的追求和平的話  就有必要思考
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準將  司令部說要給予Celestial Being何種待遇？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是討伐了已經腐敗的A-LAWS的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要他們不放棄武力  就是威脅現任政權的危險存在 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一有動靜  我們也會立即出動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別不敲門就進來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已經晉升  現在是準將了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  時間已經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角怎麼能遲到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身的克拉薩烏現在是幸福的克拉薩烏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要作為軍人而活著 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護市民  與威脅和平的存在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為父親和母親所期望的軍人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米  哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開了卡塔隆  作為Gundam Meister而生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為洛克恩·斯特拉托斯  面對這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被世界疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到懲罰降臨  我都會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟你們團聚  還得再等一等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前要等著我啊  亞琉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將再次改變 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為此我所犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走人們生命的罪孽  也絕不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界充滿了矛盾  我自己也矛盾著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  必須要做出改變才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找出我們生存的意義…以及答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣  未來就交給了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將成為吠陀的一部分  守護著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到將要到來的對話之日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界究竟會變成什麼樣子  誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我認為世界能夠有各種各樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使過去無法改變  未來卻是可以改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著我們所期望的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是走錯了路怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因悲傷的誤解而引發爭鬥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定會再次出現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使身懷所有的矛盾  也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧  我們還有要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家以生命為代價所改變的這個世界  我們要繼續守護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以根絕戰爭為目的之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被世界所拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要繼續與之對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要行使武力  也要作為世界的抑制力而生存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此  我們才必須繼續存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}人類的童年結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:24:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版  機動戰士高達00  2010年公開
