Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:18.15,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一緒に帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:54.01,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}若丟棄是為了撿回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:59.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}那分別就是為了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:05.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}告別之後　一定會
